Resource Profile: Debt Portal Patient

Official URL: http://va.gov/fhir/StructureDefinition/DebtPortalPatient Version: 1.6.49
Active as of 2025-06-13 Computable Name: DebtPortalPatient

This StructureDefinition contains the maps for VistA file ACCOUNTS RECEIVABLE (430) to Patient.

​See also the FHIR Shorthand.

Use Case Overview

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: Debt Portal Invoice and Debt Portal PaymentReconciliation
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: Lung Cancer Screening
